# Quant Trading Platform — Overview

This repo is a **professional quant trading platform** rebuilt from scratch, powered by modern tooling and disciplined methodology. It was originally a college hobby project; it is now being built properly.

## What This Is
- **One app, many algos.** A single platform housing multiple trading strategies that can be developed, tested, and run independently.
- **Paper-first.** All new strategies run on Alpaca paper trading before any real capital is committed.
- **Real money only after rigorous testing.** Capital is introduced in small increments after: out-of-sample validation, walk-forward testing, live paper performance review, and cost-adjusted profitability confirmation.
- **Cloud-ready, local-first.** Development runs on localhost. Production target: Vercel (UI) + GCP Cloud Run (engine).

## Asset Classes
Equities (primary), crypto (Coinbase), potentially other instruments over time.

## Data Sources
- `yfinance` — historical OHLCV data
- Alpaca — paper and live trading, real-time market data
- Coinbase — crypto data
- LLMs / Perplexity — sentiment and research augmentation

## The Goal
Build an analytical, honest, rigorous trading system — not a speculative toy. Every strategy must earn its place through math and evidence.
